the military.
That new policy was due five
months ago. Can

28:52.798 --> 28:56.301 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
you give us any insight into
what the issues
are that are holding this up?

28:56.335 --> 29:00.973 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RAY MABUS: I know that the
process is ongoing.
We have participated in the
process in terms

29:01.006 --> 29:02.674 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of transgender.

29:02.708 --> 29:10.148 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think that, from Secretary
Carter's
memo, when he set this out, it's
not if, but

29:10.182 --> 29:16.822 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
when. It's not if, but how. We
had all expected
the policy before now, but
things take a while

29:16.855 --> 29:17.389 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
sometimes.

29:17.422 --> 29:18.523 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JOHN YANG: Very good.

29:18.557 --> 29:21.426 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Secretary Ray Mabus, thank you
for being with
us.

29:21.460 --> 29:28.266 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
RAY MABUS: Appreciate it, John.

