30:12.310 --> 30:16.381 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: The president
and vice president's
visit today comes as the people
of Orlando

30:16.415 --> 30:20.318 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
