means a lot. It shows that the
nation is watching.

30:24.823 --> 30:31.897 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think that's the idealism at
that point,
that he's taken time, the
president has taken

30:31.930 --> 30:36.101 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
