hey, he feels
for them and is watching it.

30:36.134 --> 30:40.472 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: But, for
others, especially
those who witnessed the attack
firsthand inside

30:40.505 --> 30:44.676 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the Pulse nightclub, ceremonies
and visits
can only do so much.

30:44.710 --> 30:49.848 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Jeanette McCoy drove to the club
Saturday
night and was inside with her
friends Julian

30:49.881 --> 30:55.487 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Amador and Yvens Carrenard when
