31:02.627 --> 31:08.100 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEANETTE MCCOY, Survivor: We
lost so many
people. We lost a part of us.
People don't

31:08.133 --> 31:14.106 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
