dead, but
the ones that survived, we can't
hold a service

31:14.139 --> 31:15.974 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
for our heads.

31:16.007 --> 31:19.311 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Carrenard
can't shake the
images of what he saw as he
escaped the club.

31:19.344 --> 31:22.180 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
YVENS CARRENARD, Survivor: I
could hear people
moaning. And I could hear people
screaming

31:22.214 --> 31:26.351 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
for help. When they came and got
us, I had
to physically walk by bodies. We
had to walk

31:26.384 --> 31:29.254 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
