just where we
were standing.

31:29.287 --> 31:32.991 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: McCoy told us
today she
believes the police waited too
long to rush

31:33.024 --> 31:36.061 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in, which she says allowed it to
become a
hostage situation.

31:36.094 --> 31:41.166 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEANETTE MCCOY: Through all of
this that's
going on, the gunshots didn't
stop. They just

31:41.199 --> 31:46.004 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
didn't stop. I'm still yelling
at the cops
and telling them it made no
sense. I said,

31:46.037 --> 31:49.908 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
it's one individual in there.
How it is that
there's hundreds of cops out
there and no

31:49.941 --> 31:51.777 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
one is going in?

31:51.810 --> 31:55.213 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: But others
believe officials
did the best they could and now
is the time

31:55.247 --> 31:57.616 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to focus on the future.

31:57.649 --> 32:02.788 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Don Price is helping the city of
Orlando establish
a permanent memorial here in
Greenwood Cemetery.

32:02.821 --> 32:05.323 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
