plots for
any of the victims.

32:05.357 --> 32:10.529 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DON PRICE: A lot of these
victims are not
staying in Orlando. They're
being sent home

32:10.562 --> 32:14.666 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
