around. Their
friends and their family base is
still here

32:18.770 --> 32:23.475 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in Orlando. So we need a place
that the community
can come and grieve.

32:23.508 --> 32:27.679 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: DeAngelo Scott
was dancing
that night at Pulse, too, but he
left just

32:27.712 --> 32:32.050 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
before the attacks began. Six of
his friends
died that night.

32:32.083 --> 32:38.390 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He says the so-called Pulse
family, the whole
LGBT community, must come
together to heal

32:38.423 --> 32:40.559 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and to lead by example for the
rest of the
city.

32:40.592 --> 32:42.894 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
DEANGELO SCOTT, Orlando
Resident: We're going
to get fine. We're going to get
through this.

32:42.928 --> 32:47.599 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I was like, we don't really
have a choice.
I was like, because the Pulse
family is what

32:47.632 --> 32:50.502 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
built the overall Pulse family,
which is the
family we have in the community.

32:50.535 --> 32:54.439 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I was like, so we have to make
sure that we
fix ourselves, so that the rest
of us, the

32:54.472 --> 32:57.375 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
rest of the city, you know, can
look up to
us for support.

32:57.409 --> 33:00.178 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: That's right.
You don't
have a choice.

33:00.212 --> 33:03.782 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DEANGELO SCOTT: Yes. Otherwise,
they win.
We can't let them win.

