For an update, Gwen Ifill spoke
this week
with Amin Awad. He's the
director Middle East

33:49.027 --> 33:52.797 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and North Africa for the U.N.
Refugee Agency,
UNHCR.

33:52.831 --> 33:56.001 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Mr. Awad, welcome.

33:56.034 --> 34:00.238 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
On this program, we have seen
