stories of the hundreds of
thousands of refugees

34:00.272 --> 34:04.175 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
coming, especially from the
Mideast and Africa,
trying to get to Greece, trying
to get to

34:04.209 --> 34:06.144 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Turkey, trying to get into
Europe.

34:06.177 --> 34:10.782 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
