began?

34:10.815 --> 34:14.886 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AMIN AWAD, United Nations High
Commissioner
for Refugees: I think this
problem of migrants

34:14.920 --> 34:18.924 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
