conflict, coming
from East Africa, the Horn of
Africa, or the

35:11.443 --> 35:15.914 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
central part of Africa or the
western part
of Africa. So the root causes
for flight are

35:15.947 --> 35:20.485 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
still there. And the world has
to come up
with more mechanisms and better
mechanisms

35:20.518 --> 35:23.021 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to tackle the root causes of
these conflicts
or poverty.

35:23.054 --> 35:28.626 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: So the root causes
