international
instruments, the international
protection,

36:11.703 --> 36:17.942 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
international national refugee
law, the international
human rights law. We have to
rally around

36:17.976 --> 36:21.379 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
these and similar, because
