the world also orderly.

36:21.413 --> 36:26.084 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: But you know that,
in this country,
we're having a big presidential
debate which

36:26.117 --> 36:30.588 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
circles around in part what we
should be,
how many refugees we should be
accepting.

36:30.622 --> 36:36.127 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, in Europe, the vote, the
Brexit about
