36:38.530 --> 36:41.366 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Doesn't make your task an uphill
one?

36:41.399 --> 36:46.738 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AMIN AWAD: It does in a way,
