38:10.355 --> 38:14.826 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
AMIN AWAD: If we are to
stabilize the world
and the protracted conflicts,
resources have

38:14.859 --> 38:16.794 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
